{"data":[{"date":"15:49 26/06","title":"\"Sterling ph\u1ea3i nh\u01b0\u1eddng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh cho Rashford \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p B\u1ec9\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/26/sterling.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sam Allardyce ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Raheem Sterling, c\u1ef1u HLV tuy\u1ec3n Anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh HLV Gareth Southgate c\u1ea7n lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Man City \u0111\u1ec3 trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho Raheem Sterling.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Raheem Sterling g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Anh \u1edf World Cup 2018, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Raheem Sterling \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh. Ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1994 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Gareth Southgate b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 c\u1eb7p ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o v\u1edbi Harry Kane trong s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 3-5-2.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sam Allardyce ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Raheem Sterling h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Sam Allardyce ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Raheem Sterling h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/21/Sam-Allardyce-phat-bieu-ve-Raheem-Sterling-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Sterling \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Southgate trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i nh\u01b0ng g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 Harry Kane ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t v\u1edbi 5 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u00ec Sterling l\u1ea1i g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn. \u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Tunisia c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i, nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ed9t ph\u00e1 c\u1ee7a anh c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111em l\u1ea1i hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Panama, Sterling c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n. V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u. Kh\u00f4ng \u00edt \u00fd ki\u1ebfn cho r\u1eb1ng HLV Gareth Southgate n\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Man City ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, trong m\u1ed9t bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp HLV Southgate \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ed9 m\u1ed9t s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt, theo \u0111\u00f3 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/ro-ri-doi-hinh-anh-gap-panama-sterling-lam-nguy-421-189246.html\" target=\"_blank\">Sterling ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Panama</span>, nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i anh v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Sam Allardyce mu\u1ed1n Rashford thay th\u1ebf Sterling</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sam Allardyce ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Raheem Sterling, c\u1ef1u HLV tuy\u1ec3n Anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh HLV Gareth Southgate c\u1ea7n lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Man City \u0111\u1ec3 trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho Rashford.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Big Sam cho rang Sterling phai ngoi du bi cho Rashford\" title=\"Big Sam cho r\u1eb1ng Sterling ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb cho Rashford\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/26/sterling.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Big Sam cho r\u1eb1ng Sterling ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb cho Rashford</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 l\u00fd do n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 Gareth Southgate ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c tin t\u01b0\u1edfng Sterling, 2 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp l\u00e0 qu\u00e1 \u0111\u1ee7 r\u1ed3i. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u01b0 trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Man City, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;Rashford \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu tr\u01b0\u1edbc World Cup 2018, \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00fac c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng ngay t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n Gareth Southgate trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho Rashford, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"608","checkdouble":"189625"},{"date":"16:02 26/06","title":"Wenger ch\u1ec9 ra m\u1eaft x\u00edch y\u1ebfu k\u00e9m nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/19/wenger-chi-ra-mat-xich-yeu-kem-nhat-cua-dt-anh.PNG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Arsene Wenger ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Anh, c\u1ef1u HLV Arsenal kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Kyle Walker l\u00e0 m\u1eaft x\u00edch y\u1ebfu nh\u1ea5t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Tam s\u01b0 \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kyle Walker kh\u00f4ng \u0111em l\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, Kyle Walker l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea1t phong \u0111\u1ed9 cao nh\u1ea5t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Man City. Ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1990 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Gareth Southgate b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh trong hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Tam s\u01b0 \u1edf World Cup 2018.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Arsene Wenger ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Anh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Arsene Wenger ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Anh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/13/Arsene-Wenger-phat-bieu-ve-DT-Anh-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Kyle Walker ch\u01a1i thi\u1ebfu \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh trong hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Anh \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 3-5-2, Walker \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh Harry Maguire v\u00e0 John Stones \u1edf h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi. Trong s\u1ed1 3 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Gareth Southgate tin t\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Tunisia ch\u00ednh <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/kyle-walker-cau-thu-thuy-si-tu-lao-vao-cui-cho-cua-toi-469-188898.html\" target=\"_blank\">Walker l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i khi\u1ebfn Anh ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn 1 qu\u1ea3 11m</span>, \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Panama c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u0169ng th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean b\u1ecf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed. M\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n thi\u1ebfu \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1990 khi\u1ebfn NHM S\u01b0 t\u1eed Anh r\u1ea5t lo l\u1eafng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nS\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1eddng c\u1ee7a Walker l\u00e0 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i trong h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 4 ng\u01b0\u1eddi, khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 trong h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c cho th\u1ea5y nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Wenger kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao Walker</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Arsene Wenger ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Anh, c\u1ef1u HLV Arsenal kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Kyle Walker l\u00e0 m\u1eaft x\u00edch y\u1ebfu nh\u1ea5t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Tam s\u01b0 \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kyle Walker\" title=\"Kyle Walker\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/19/wenger-chi-ra-mat-xich-yeu-kem-nhat-cua-dt-anh.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Wenger \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 kh\u00f4ng cao Kyle Walker trong h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;C\u1eadu \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i trong m\u1ed9t h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p trong vai tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7. Southgate n\u00ean t\u1ea1o ra s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi qu\u00e1 mu\u1ed9n. Anh v\u1eabn c\u00f2n Eric Dier, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 trung v\u1ec7 r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t, Dier h\u1ee3p h\u01a1n l\u00e0 Walker trong h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;Nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Anh \u1edf 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao, nh\u01b0ng Walker \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ed9c l\u1ed9 nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1. Khi g\u1eb7p nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd c\u00f2n ch\u01a1i t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i h\u01a1n n\u1eefa, t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng Southgate c\u1ea7n t\u1ea1o ra s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i c\u00e0ng nhanh c\u00e0ng t\u1ed1t&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;Walker \u0111ang l\u00e0 m\u1eaft x\u00edch y\u1ebfu nh\u1ea5t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Anh, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd n\u1ebfu c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m khi bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1 \u1edf h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng g\u1ed3m 3&nbsp;h\u1eadu v\u1ec7&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"607","checkdouble":"189626"},{"date":"16:11 26/06","title":"5 s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt gi\u00fap Argentina h\u1ea1 Nigeria \u0111\u1ec3 m\u01a1 v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/26/5-so-do-chien-thuat-giup-argentina-ha-nigeria-de-mo-ve-di-tiep.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Arsenal mua Lewis Dunk th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng cao. Theo Mirror, HLV Unai Emery kh\u00f4ng h\u1ee9ng th\u00fa v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 chuy\u1ec3n sang nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau kh\u00e1c.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Arsene Wenger t\u1eebng quan t\u00e2m Lewis Dunk</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, trung v\u1ec7 Lewis Dunk l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1ea5t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Brighton.\u00a0<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Arsenal mua Lewis Dunk th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng cao h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Arsenal mua Lewis Dunk th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng cao h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/26/arsenal-nham-sao-brighton-nang-cap-hang-thu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Wenger t\u1eebng mu\u1ed1n Arsenal mua Lewis Dunk</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNg\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1991 ra s\u00e2n trong c\u1ea3 38 tr\u1eadn \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh, m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do gi\u00fap Brighton tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nLewis Dunk c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u1ed1ng b\u00f3ng b\u1ed5ng t\u1ed1t, anh c\u0169ng li\u00ean k\u1ebft c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i. HLV Arsene Wenger \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i, \u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n BL\u0110 Arsenal \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong danh s\u00e1ch nh\u1eefng t\u00e2n binh m\u00e0 Arsenal mu\u1ed1n mua \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, Lewis Dunk l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u. \u201cGi\u00e1o s\u01b0\u201d nh\u1eafm c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1991 nh\u01b0 s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf l\u00e2u d\u00e0i cho Laurent Koscielny.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nArsenal th\u1eadm ch\u00ed \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch chi 22 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh, h\u1ecd hy v\u1ecdng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00f4i k\u00e9o c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh t\u1edbi s\u00e2n Emrates.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Arsenal t\u1eeb b\u1ecf Lewis Dunk</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Arsenal mua Lewis Dunk th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng cao. Theo Mirror, HLV Unai Emery kh\u00f4ng h\u1ee9ng th\u00fa v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 chuy\u1ec3n sang nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau kh\u00e1c.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lewis Dunk\" title=\"Lewis Dunk\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/7/dunk.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Arsenal t\u1eeb b\u1ecf Lewis Dunk v\u00ec Emery kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ef1u HLV PSG kh\u00f4ng th\u00edch phong c\u00e1ch thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Lewis Dunk, \u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Sokratis c\u1ee7a Dortmund h\u01a1n l\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Brighton. Theo nhi\u1ec1u ngu\u1ed3n tin, Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 17 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u1ecfi mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Hy L\u1ea1p.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/arsenal-tra-gia-dat-koscielny-chan-thuong-nang-mat-world-cup-184-185546.html\" target=\"_blank\">Laurent Koscielny d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u1eb7ng</span> v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ebfn th\u00e1ng 12 m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i, b\u1edfi v\u1eady HLV Emery bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e1 c\u1eb7p trung v\u1ec7 v\u1edbi Mustafi.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nArsenal v\u1eabn c\u00f2n \u0111\u00f3 Chambers hay Holding, song nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 trong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o h\u1ecd l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 m\u1ea1o hi\u1ec3m r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"606","checkdouble":"189628"},{"date":"16:03 26/06","title":"Nh\u1eefng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1ec1 C\u0110V n\u1eef Iran khoe s\u1eafc t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/26/1368684.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>S\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a C\u0110V n\u1eef Iran t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 mang \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t m\u00e0u s\u1eafc \u0111\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e1o b\u1edfi v\u1edbi r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ph\u1ee5 n\u1eef Iran, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean h\u1ecd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00e0o s\u00e2n c\u1ed5 v\u0169 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1.</h2><div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eefng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1ec1 C\u0110V n\u1eef Iran t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eefng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1ec1 C\u0110V n\u1eef Iran t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/26/Nhung-hinh-anh-an-tuong-ve-CDV-nu-Iran-tai-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>K\u1ec3 t\u1eeb n\u0103m 1980, Iran ban b\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ea1o lu\u1eadt kh\u00f4ng cho ph\u00e9p ph\u1ee5 n\u1eef v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e0n \u00f4ng c\u00f9ng v\u00e0o s\u00e2n trong m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<b