ha-421-189570.html\">HLV Santos n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a may m\u1eafn c\u1ee7a B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/bat-luc-hlv-iran-len-tieng-doi-the-do-cho-ronaldo-421-189569.html\">B\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c, HLV Iran l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng \u0111\u00f2i th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf cho Ronaldo</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/diem-nhan-iran-vs-bo-dao-nha-noi-that-vong-ronaldo-421-189568.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n Iran vs B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha: N\u1ed7i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng Ronaldo</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nN.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div>\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"605","checkdouble":"189631"},{"date":"16:31 26/06","title":"Juventus ch\u1ed1t gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n Alex Sandro cho MU","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/18/juventus-chot-gia-ban-alex-sandro-cho-mu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Juventus b\u00e1n Alex Sandro v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 52,8 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n n\u00e0y MU ho\u1eb7c Chelsea s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">MU th\u00e8m kh\u00e1t Alex Sandro</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Alex Sandro ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a Juventus \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1991 c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng l\u00ean c\u00f4ng v\u1ec1 th\u1ee7 r\u1ea5t nh\u1ecbp nh\u00e0ng, \u1edf tu\u1ed5i 27 anh c\u0169ng c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kinh nghi\u1ec7m thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ec9nh cao.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"MU ch\u00fa \u00fd Juventus b\u00e1n Alex Sandro v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 52,8 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"MU ch\u00fa \u00fd Juventus b\u00e1n Alex Sandro v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 52,8 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/18/juventus-chot-gia-ban-alex-sandro-cho-mu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>MU r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Alex Sandro</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nMourinho \u0111ang c\u1ea7n ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf l\u00e2u d\u00e0i cho Young, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u0103m nay \u0111\u00e3 33 tu\u1ed5i. Vi\u1ec7c Luke Shaw kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Old Trafford l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n s\u1edf h\u1eefu Alex Sandro c\u1ee7a Juventus.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y b\u00e1o ch\u00ed \u0111\u1ed3n th\u1ed5i r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/day-muc-tieu-so-1-cua-mu-o-vi-tri-hau-ve-trai-172-182680.html\" target=\"_blank\">MU mu\u1ed1n Mua Sandro</span>, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford c\u00f2n ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi t\u1edbi 40 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. Chelsea c\u0169ng quan t\u00e2m ng\u00f4i sao 27 tu\u1ed5i, song M.U l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m h\u01a1n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nThe Sun kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh M.U \u0111\u00e3 c\u1eed ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ebfn Italia \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n, Mourinho mu\u1ed1n BL\u0110 \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1991.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Juventus \u0111\u00f2i 52,8 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho Sandro</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Juventus b\u00e1n Alex Sandro v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 52,8 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n n\u00e0y MU ho\u1eb7c Chelsea s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Alex Sandro\" title=\"Alex Sandro\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/18/mu-tu-choi-mua-sao-khung-juventus-voi-gia-53-trieu-bang.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Juventus \u0111\u00f2i 52,8 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho Alex Sandro</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn trao \u0111\u1ed5i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 mu\u1ed1n nh\u1eadn ti\u1ec1n m\u1eb7t trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. S\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n m\u00e0 Juventus \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi&nbsp;l\u1edbn h\u01a1n kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u so v\u1edbi kho\u1ea3n ph\u00ed m\u00e0 M.U d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh chi ra.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo \u0111\u00f3, M.U d\u1ef1 t\u00ednh chi t\u1ed1i \u0111a 40 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng t\u0103ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Juventus \u0111\u00f2i t\u1edbi 52,8 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, M.U s\u1ebd bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin ho\u1eb7c chuy\u1ec3n sang m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau kh\u00e1c.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMirror kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi c\u1ee7a Juventus, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/mu-mua-jose-gaya-cua-valencia-172-182126.html\" target=\"_blank\">M.U chuy\u1ec3n sang Jose Gaya c\u1ee7a Valencia</span> thay v\u00ec b\u1ecf ra 52,8 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1991.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"604","checkdouble":"189632"},{"date":"17:00 26/06","title":"Th\u1ef1c h\u01b0 v\u1ee5 Arsenal nh\u1eafm sao Brighton n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/26/arsenal-nham-sao-brighton-nang-cap-hang-thu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Arsenal mua Lewis Dunk th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng cao. Theo Mirror, HLV Unai Emery kh\u00f4ng h\u1ee9ng th\u00fa v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 chuy\u1ec3n sang nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau kh\u00e1c.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Arsene Wenger t\u1eebng quan t\u00e2m Lewis Dunk</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, trung v\u1ec7 Lewis Dunk l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1ea5t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Brighton.\u00a0<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Arsenal mua Lewis Dunk th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng cao h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Arsenal mua Lewis Dunk th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng cao h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/26/arsenal-nham-sao-brighton-nang-cap-hang-thu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Wenger t\u1eebng mu\u1ed1n Arsenal mua Lewis Dunk</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNg\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1991 ra s\u00e2n trong c\u1ea3 38 tr\u1eadn \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh, m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do gi\u00fap Brighton tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nLewis Dunk c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u1ed1ng b\u00f3ng b\u1ed5ng t\u1ed1t, anh c\u0169ng li\u00ean k\u1ebft c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i. HLV Arsene Wenger \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i, \u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n BL\u0110 Arsenal \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong danh s\u00e1ch nh\u1eefng t\u00e2n binh m\u00e0 Arsenal mu\u1ed1n mua \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, Lewis Dunk l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u. \u201cGi\u00e1o s\u01b0\u201d nh\u1eafm c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1991 nh\u01b0 s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf l\u00e2u d\u00e0i cho Laurent Koscielny.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nArsenal th\u1eadm ch\u00ed \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch chi 22 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh, h\u1ecd hy v\u1ecdng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00f4i k\u00e9o c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh t\u1edbi s\u00e2n Emrates.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Arsenal t\u1eeb b\u1ecf Lewis Dunk</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Arsenal mua Lewis Dunk th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng cao. Theo Mirror, HLV Unai Emery kh\u00f4ng h\u1ee9ng th\u00fa v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 chuy\u1ec3n sang nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau kh\u00e1c.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lewis Dunk\" title=\"Lewis Dunk\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/7/dunk.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Arsenal t\u1eeb b\u1ecf Lewis Dunk v\u00ec Emery kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ef1u HLV PSG kh\u00f4ng th\u00edch phong c\u00e1ch thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Lewis Dunk, \u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Sokratis c\u1ee7a Dortmund h\u01a1n l\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Brighton. Theo nhi\u1ec1u ngu\u1ed3n tin, Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 17 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u1ecfi mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Hy L\u1ea1p.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/arsenal-tra-gia-dat-koscielny-chan-thuong-nang-mat-world-cup-184-185546.html\" target=\"_blank\">Laurent Koscielny d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u1eb7ng</span> v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ebfn th\u00e1ng 12 m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i, b\u1edfi v\u1eady HLV Emery bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e1 c\u1eb7p trung v\u1ec7 v\u1edbi Mustafi.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nArsenal v\u1eabn c\u00f2n \u0111\u00f3 Chambers hay Holding, song nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 trong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o h\u1ecd l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 m\u1ea1o hi\u1ec3m r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"603","checkdouble":"189633"},{"date":"16:20 26/06","title":"Nh\u1eefng d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u \u0111inh Ph\u00e1p vs \u0110an M\u1ea1ch","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/26/truc-tiep-dan-mach-vs-phap.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Ph\u00e1p vs \u0110an M\u1ea1ch c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 nghi ng\u1edd d\u00e0nh cho \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch. Tuy nhi\u00ean, th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf l\u00e0 ngay c\u1ea3 khi c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t, nh\u1eefng nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb c\u00f3 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Les Bleus v\u1eabn s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>L\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- <strong>Nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng</strong> (t\u1eeb 2 tr\u1edf l\u00ean)<br>\r\nD\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1: Ph\u00e1p th\u1eafng 2-1<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<em>Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u: </em>Ph\u00e1p vs \u0110an M\u1ea1ch<br>\r\n<em>Th\u1eddi gian:</em> 21h ng\u00e0y 26/6<br>\r\n<em>\u0110\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m: </em>S\u00e2n Luzhniki (Moskva)<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>TLCA c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn: </em>Ph\u00e1p 0.86*0:1/2*0.81 \u0110an M\u1ea1ch<br>\r\n<em>TBT c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn: </em>Nhi\u1ec1u 0.93*2*1.00 \u00cdt<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Ph\u00e1p vs \u0110an M\u1ea1ch v\u00e0 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n v\u00e0ng tr\u00ean Bongda24h h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Ph\u00e1p vs \u0110an M\u1ea1ch v\u00e0 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n v\u00e0ng tr\u00ean Bongda24h h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/26/nhan-dinh-phap-vs-dan-mach-va-du-doan-soi-keo-dan-mach-vs-phap.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Ph\u00e1p vs \u0110an M\u1ea1ch 21h ng\u00e0y 26/6</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 tr\u00f4i qua ch\u01b0a th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o d\u00e0nh cho \u0110T Ph\u00e1p. L\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t, h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Australia 2-1 v\u00e0 Peru 1-0. \u0110\u00f3 r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng ch\u01b0a ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh t\u01b0\u01a1ng x\u1ee9ng v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch c\u1ee7a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, s\u1ef1 th\u1ef1c l\u00e0 Ph\u00e1p v\u1eabn c\u00f3 tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n 6 \u0111i\u1ec3m sau 2 l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn, \u0111\u00f3 m\u1edbi l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t. \u0110\u1ec3 \u0111i \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng d\u00e0i, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n bung s\u1ee9c qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ec3 r\u1ed3i h\u1ee5t h\u01a1i v\u00e0o giai \u0111o\u1ea1n then ch\u1ed1t. L\u1ecbch s\u1eed ch\u1ee9ng minh kh\u00f4ng \u00edt \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u0103ng quang t\u1ea1i World Cup d\u00f9 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u m\u1edd nh\u1ea1t t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Australia thua dau Phap\" title=\"Australia thua dau Phap\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/21/Australia-thua-dau-Phap.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Ph\u00e1p kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u World Cup 2018 kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1eabn c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u00e1ng t\u1eeb Ph\u00e1p sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Peru, \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean l\u00e0 t\u1eeb c\u00e1ch d\u1ee5ng binh c\u1ee7a HLV Didier Deschamps. \u0110\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 s\u1ef1 \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh t\u1eeb thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Les Bleus \u0111i\u1ec3n h\u00ecnh l\u00e0 c\u00e1ch \u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0a Olivier Giroud l\u00ean \u0111\u00e1 c\u1eafm \u0111\u1ec3 Antoine Griezmann \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i t\u1ef1 do h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i ra, vi\u1ec7c t\u00edch h\u1ee3p Blaise Matuidi v\u00e0o h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 thay cho Corentin Tolisso c\u0169ng gi\u00fap Paul Pogba \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng kh\u1ecfi nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ec3 Ph\u00e1p c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng kh\u1edfi s\u1eafc so v\u1edbi tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n v\u1edbi Australia.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/goc-nhin-world-cup-2018/3-ly-do-giup-dt-phap-nhe-nhang-vuot-qua-peru-466-189269.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/22/3-ly-do-giup-dt-phap-nhe-nhang-vuot-qua-peru.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/goc-nhin-world-cup-2018/3-ly-do-giup-dt-phap-nhe-nhang-vuot-qua-peru-466-189269.html\">3 l\u00fd do gi\u00fap \u0110T Ph\u00e1p nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Peru</span><br>\r\n<span>Sau m\u1ed9t m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n b\u1ea1c nh\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Australia, Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u tr\u01b0\u1edbc Peru. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do gi\u00fap Les Bleus gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n c\u00f9ng su\u1ea5t...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1eefng tr\u1ee5c tr\u1eb7c xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n s\u1edbm l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u00edch c\u1ef1c. N\u00f3 gi\u00fap HLV Deschamps s\u1edbm nh\u00ecn ra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p v\u00e0 r\u1ed3i s\u1eeda ch\u1eefa. Ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p h\u1ecd r\u01a1i v\u00e0o tr\u1ea1ng th\u00e1i t\u1ef1 m\u00e3n \u0111\u1ec3 r\u1ed3i ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 gi\u00e1 \u0111\u1eaft.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y, nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Ph\u00e1p vs \u0110an M\u1ea1ch s\u1ebd c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 chuy\u1ec3n bi\u1ebfn l\u1edbn. Sau khi ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn c\u00f3 v\u00e9 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng knock-out, t\u00e2m l\u00fd &ldquo;B\u1ea7y g\u00e0 tr\u1ed1ng&rdquo; s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng. H\u1ecd h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n b\u1eaft m\u1eaft tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110an M\u1ea1ch \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec1 cho nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cam go s\u1eafp \u0111\u1ebfn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Pogba Griezmann\" title=\"Pogba Griezmann\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/25/bai-du-thi-an-tuong-world-cup-2018-messi-khong-biet-coi-ao-va-bay-thang-len-troi-vay-tai-sao-chung-ta-lai-bat-anh-ay-phai-lam-sieu-nhan.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Ni\u1ec1m vui \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi \u0110T&nbsp;Ph\u00e1p</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Ph\u00e1p s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t. Kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 y\u00eau c\u1ea7u h\u1ecd tung ra y nguy\u00ean 11 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh, song v\u1eabn c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 m\u1eaft x\u00edch then ch\u1ed1t. H\u01a1n n\u1eefa, chi\u1ec1u s\u00e2u \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u ph\u1ea3i c\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u00f9 Thomas Lemar, Nabil Fekir hay Steven N'Zonzi xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 thua k\u00e9m nhi\u1ec1u so v\u1edbi Kylian Mbappe, Ousmane Dembele hay Matuidi. Th\u00eam n\u1eefa, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111ang r\u1ea5t kh\u00e1t khao ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh tr\u00ean s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i World Cup.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKhi c\u1ea3 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o, t\u1ef1 kh\u1eafc c\u00e1c tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Ph\u00e1p s\u1ebd c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c cho m\u00ecnh. Nh\u00ecn to\u00e0n c\u1ee5c, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng c\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng. 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ee7 cho \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 song kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean n\u1ebfu HLV Deschamps ra m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau ph\u1ea3i th\u1eafng cho c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2. M\u1ed9t m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng s\u1ebd g\u00f3p ph\u1ea7n n\u00e2ng cao s\u0129 kh\u00ed c\u1ee7a \u0110T Ph\u00e1p.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Didier Deschamps\" title=\"Didier Deschamps\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/26/gettyimages-9750651941-1024x704.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Deschamps \u0111ang c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i v\u1ec1 t\u00e2m l\u00fd</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110an M\u1ea1ch c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i ch\u01b0\u1edbng ng\u1ea1i g\u00ec to t\u00e1t. \u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn tr\u01b0\u1edbc, h\u1ecd v\u1ea5t v\u1ea3 m\u1edbi h\u00f2a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Australia 1-1. Sau tr\u1eadn, HLV Bert van Marwijk c\u1ee7a Australia ph\u1ea3i th\u1ed1t l\u00ean: &ldquo;<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/hlv-australia-tiec-nuoi-sau-tran-hoa-dan-mach-465-189184.html\" target=\"_blank\">L\u1ebd ra \u0111\u1ebfn gi\u1edd n\u00e0y Australia ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 4 \u0111i\u1ec3m</span>&rdquo;. Theo \u00f4ng, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ed1i \u0111a tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110an M\u1ea1ch thay v\u00ec ch\u1ec9 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1eadt v\u1eady, \u0110an M\u1ea1ch ch\u1ec9 bi\u1ebft co c\u1ee5m ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf b\u00e0n thua. Trong kh\u00e2u t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, h\u1ecd ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0o Christian Eriksen. N\u1ebfu b\u00f3ng kh\u00f4ng trong ch\u00e2n c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao thu\u1ed9c bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf Tottenham, l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ee3t t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a &ldquo;Nh\u1eefng ch\u00fa l\u00ednh ch\u00ec&rdquo; \u0111i v\u00e0o ng\u00f5 c\u1ee5t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Peru vs Dan Mach Schone di bong\" title=\"Peru vs Dan Mach Schone di bong\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/17/nhung-thong-ke-an-tuong-sau-tran-dau-dan-mach-10-peru.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u0110an M\u1ea1ch c\u00f2n nhi\u1ec1u h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u1ea7y s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng k\u00e9m ph\u1ea7n t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o, nh\u1eefng pha x\u1eed l\u00fd thi\u1ebfu m\u1ec1m m\u1ea1i, tinh t\u1ebf c\u1ee7a \u0110an M\u1ea1ch c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 gi\u00e1 \u0111\u1eaft. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc Australia, h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i h\u1ee9ng ch\u1ecbu \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1ec9 v\u00ec \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 thi\u1ebfu tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 may m\u1eafn m\u00e0 th\u00f4i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Ph\u00e1p, \u0110an M\u1ea1ch s\u1ebd tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m th\u1eed th\u00e1ch l\u1edbn h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u so v\u1edbi Peru hay Australia. M\u1ed9t k\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra: \u0110an M\u1ea1ch c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f4ng v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ea7u h\u00f2a nh\u01b0ng s\u1edbm b\u1ecb ch\u1ecdc th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi. T\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd ph\u1ea3i d\u1ed3n \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh l\u00ean cao v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, song kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng d\u00ednh \u0111\u00f2n &ldquo;h\u1ed3i m\u00e3 th\u01b0\u01a1ng&rdquo; c\u00f2n cao h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGi\u1edbi d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n ch\u00e2u \u00c1 \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ed1c 2 b\u00e0n ch\u1eb5n khi nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Ph\u00e1p vs \u0110an M\u1ea1ch. Tuy nhi\u00ean, v\u1edbi s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p, ch\u1ec9 ri\u00eang m\u00ecnh h\u1ecd c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 san b\u1eb1ng ho\u1eb7c v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua c\u1ed9t m\u1ed1c n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>L\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- <strong>Nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng</strong> (t\u1eeb 2 tr\u1edf l\u00ean)<br>\r\nD\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1: Ph\u00e1p th\u1eafng 2-1<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t kh\u00e1c</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- T\u1ed5ng s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1ebd l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 l\u1ebb<br>\r\n- Hai \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi<br>\r\n- S\u1ed1 qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p s\u1ebd nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 1 (-3/4)<br>\r\n- S\u1ed1 qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c hi\u1ec7p 1 c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p s\u1ebd nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 1 (-1/2)<br>\r\n- T\u1ed5ng s\u1ed1 qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn c\u1ee7a hai \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 9 (U 9 1/2)<br>\r\n- T\u1ed5ng s\u1ed1 th\u1ebb ph\u1ea1t c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn c\u1ee7a hai \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 3 (U 3)<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u1ea3i Ly (TTVN)<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"602","checkdouble":"189634"},{"date":"17:11 26/06","title":"3 l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 tin Argentina v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Nigeria v\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/26/bai-du-thi-an-tuong-world-cup-2018-trong-tai-thoi-cong-nghe-40-thuan-loi-va-thach-thuc.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nigeria \u0111ang c\u00f3 t\u00e2m l\u00fd t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n Argentina tr\u01b0\u1edbc cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 s\u1eafp t\u1edbi b\u1edfi 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Messi s\u1ebd gi\u00fap \u2018nh\u1eefng ch\u00fa \u0111\u1ea1i b\u00e0ng xanh\u2019 c\u1ea7m ch\u1eafc t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp. Tuy nhi\u00ean v\u1eabn c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 tin Argentina s\u1ebd v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Nigeria v\u00e0 c\u00f3 v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ee5c di\u1ec7n b\u1ea3ng D sau l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 hai \u0111ang di\u1ec5n ra kh\u00e1 c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng b\u1edfi ngo\u00e0i \u0110T Croatia \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn c\u00f3 v\u00e9 v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng knock-out sau hai tr\u1eadn to\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u00ec c\u1ea3 Nigeria, Iceland v\u00e0 Argentina v\u1eabn c\u00f2n nguy\u00ean c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ebfp cu\u1ed1i, Messi v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i hi\u1ec3u r\u1eb1ng m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng th\u1eadt \u0111\u1eadm \u1edf tr\u1eadn <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-nigeria-vs-argentina-1h00-ngay-276-vua-da-bong-vua-cau-nguyen-421-189578.html\" target=\"_blank\">Argentina vs Nigeria\u00a0</span>s\u1ebd c\u1ea7m ch\u1eafc c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp. V\u00e0 \u0111\u00e2u l\u00e0 l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 tin nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim \u00e1 qu\u00e2n s\u1ebd th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y?<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>1. \u0110\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a Albiceleste<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i, Argentina \u0111ang l\u00e0 n\u1ed7i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i VCK World Cup n\u0103m nay. \u1ede ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i 1-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u00e2n binh\u2008Iceland, r\u1ed3i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n m\u1ed9t b\u1ed9 m\u1eb7t b\u1ea1c nh\u01b0\u1ee3c trong tr\u1eadn thua tan n\u00e1t Croatia v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 0-3 \u1edf lo\u1ea1t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 hai. T\u1eeb m\u1ed9t \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u, l\u00fac n\u00e0y Argentina \u0111ang \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc nguy c\u01a1 s\u1edbm b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i ngay t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng\u2008b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Argentina vs Nigeria 3 l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 tin Argentina v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Nigeria h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Argentina vs Nigeria 3 l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 tin Argentina v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Nigeria h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/26/bai-du-thi-an-tuong-world-cup-2018-trong-tai-thoi-cong-nghe-40-thuan-loi-va-thach-thuc.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Argentina lu\u00f4n bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch v\u01b0\u1ee3t kh\u00f3 \u1edf nh\u1eefng th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ebfn b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iceland v\u00e0 Croatia nh\u01b0ng Argentina v\u1eabn c\u00f3 quy\u1ec1n m\u01a1 t\u1edbi v\u00f2ng 16 \u0111\u1ed9i sau khi Nigeria c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-0 kh\u00e1 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1edbi t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea3o b\u0103ng Iceland \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 hai. C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Nigeria tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iceland \u0111\u00e3 mang t\u1edbi c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00e0ng cho \u2018nh\u1eefng v\u0169 c\u00f4n Tango\u2019.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">K\u00e9m Nigeria 2 \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u00e0 b\u1eb1ng \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u1edbi Iceland nh\u01b0ng \u0110T Argentina ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 quy\u1ec1n t\u1ef1 quy\u1ebft t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp n\u1ebfu th\u1eafng \u1edf \u2018tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft\u2019 s\u1eafp t\u1edbi v\u1edbi ch\u00ednh \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n t\u1edbi t\u1eeb ch\u00e2u Phi Nigeria, k\u00e8m \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n Croatia kh\u00f4ng bu\u00f4ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iceland.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea5m v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp s\u1ebd l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 Argentina ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi tinh th\u1ea7n quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m cao nh\u1ea5t nh\u1eb1m b\u00f9 \u0111\u1eafp cho nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng \u0111\u00e3 qua c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i th\u1ec3 di\u1ec7n cho b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Argentina. Quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m \u0111\u00e1 ho\u1eb7c v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1ebd l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c th\u00fac \u0111\u1ea9y \u0111\u1ec3 Messi v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi tr\u00ean 100% s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u00f9ng t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 th\u00f4ng h\u00e0nh v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-nigeria-vs-argentina-1h00-ngay-276-vua-da-bong-vua-cau-nguyen-421-189578.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/26/HLV-Gernot-Rohr-noi-ve-tran-Nigeria-vs-Argentina-hinh-anh.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-nigeria-vs-argentina-1h00-ngay-276-vua-da-bong-vua-cau-nguyen-421-189578.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Nigeria vs Argentina (1h00 ng\u00e0y 27/6): V\u1eeba \u0111\u00e1 b\u00f3ng, v\u1eeba c\u1ea7u nguy\u1ec7n</span><br>\r\nNh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Nigeria vs Argentina b\u1ea3ng D World Cup 2018: Th\u1eafng c\u0169ng ch\u01b0a ch\u1eafc \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ee7, Messi v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i qu\u00e1 hi\u1ec3u \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea5y, nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f2n c\u00e1ch n\u00e0o...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>2. Argentina lu\u00f4n bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch v\u01b0\u1ee3t kh\u00f3 <o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, Argentina t\u1eebng thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 tr\u1ed3i s\u1ee5t v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 v\u00e9 sang Nga tr\u01b0\u1edbc l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i. Tuy nhi\u00ean \u1edf tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u quan tr\u1ecdng n\u00e0y, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh v\u01b0\u1ee3t kh\u00f3. \u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00f3, ch\u00ednh Leo Messi \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng v\u1edbi 1 c\u00fa hat-trick v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Ecuador, gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 s\u1edf Tango gi\u00e0nh th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i chung cu\u1ed9c 3-1 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 v\u00e9 t\u1edbi n\u01b0\u1edbc Nga.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nigeria ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc Argentina s\u1ebd c\u1ea7m ch\u1eafc t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp v\u00e0 v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u Phi c\u00f3 l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ea5u ph\u00e1p ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 v\u00e0 ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Messi va dong doi tich cuc tap luyen cho tran cau sinh tu gap Nigeria\" title=\"Messi v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i t\u00edch c\u1ef1c t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n cho tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u sinh t\u1eed g\u1eb7p Nigeria\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/26/messi-va-dong-doi-tich-cuc-tap-luyen-cho-tran-cau-sinh-tu-gap-nigeria.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Messi v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i t\u00edch c\u1ef1c t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n cho tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u sinh t\u1eed g\u1eb7p Nigeria</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean n\u00ean nh\u1edb r\u1eb1ng Argentina c\u00f3 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p cao h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n Nigeria v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao l\u1edbn.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 4 n\u0103m, khi Argentina v\u00e0 Nigeria g\u1eb7p nhau t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng World Cup 2014, ch\u00ednh Messi c\u0169ng ghi 1 c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, bao g\u1ed3m m\u1ed9t c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap Albiceleste \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u2018nh\u1eefng ch\u00fa \u0111\u1ea1i b\u00e0ng xanh\u2019. V\u00e0 v\u1edbi \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, Messi ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u00e1i hi\u1ec7n \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng quan tr\u1ecdng s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/ban-thang-argentina-vs-croatia-461-189198.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/22/20180621T195318Z_273911651_RC1220A4E800_RTRMADP_3_SOCCERWORLDCUPARGCRO.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/ban-thang-argentina-vs-croatia-461-189198.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Argentina 0-3 Croatia (B\u1ea3ng D World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nTh\u1eafng Argentina 3-0 h\u00f4m 21/6, Croatia s\u1edbm gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi khi\u1ebfn Messi v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi hi\u1ec3m ho\u1ea1 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i ngay sau v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>3. Nigeria kh\u00f4ng gi\u1ecfi ch\u1ecbu s\u1ee9c \u00e9p<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u ch\u00e2u Phi nh\u01b0ng r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng Nigeria kh\u00f3 l\u00f2ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u00f4i c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t Argentina \u0111ang s\u1edf h\u1eefu nhi\u1ec1u ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng \u1edf nh\u1eefng CLB h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong lo\u1ea1t tr\u1eadn chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho World Cup 2018, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a HLV Gernot Rohr \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc CH S\u00e9c, Anh v\u00e0 Serbia. \u0110i\u1ec3m chung c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn thua n\u00e0y l\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a l\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ecba \u0111en \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ecbu n\u1ed5i nhi\u1ec7t tr\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1ee9c \u00e9p qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn t\u1eeb h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u00e2u \u00c2u.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Musa an mung cung dong doi Nigeria\" title=\"Musa an mung cung dong doi Nigeria\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/23/nigeria-20-iceland-dai-bang-cuu-song-argentina-va-messi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Nigeria kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng gi\u1ecfi ch\u1ecbu \u0111\u1ef1ng</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t Argentina b\u1eaft bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i th\u1eafng, \u0110T Nigeria c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u1eb7p v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 l\u1edbn h\u01a1n b\u1edfi h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi d\u00e0n sao t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 nguy hi\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a Albiceleste. Messi v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng ch\u1ee9ng minh nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iceland v\u00e0 Croatia ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tai n\u1ea1n v\u00e0 h\u1ecd s\u1ebd tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch \u1edf s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i World Cup.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, Nigeria t\u1eebng \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 Argentina 3 l\u1ea7n \u1edf\u00a0s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i World Cup (2002, 2010 v\u00e0 2014). \u0110\u1eb7c \u0111i\u1ec3m chung c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y l\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c \u1edf c\u1ea3 3 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n ch\u00e2u Phi \u0111\u1ec1u n\u1ebfm m\u00f9i th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i. Do \u0111\u00f3, khi m\u00e0 s\u1ee9c \u00e9p kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 thua \u0111ang \u0111\u1eb7t n\u1eb7ng l\u00ean \u0111\u00f4i vai c\u1ee7a Ahmed Musa v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i, h\u1ecd ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 m\u1eafc nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m tai h\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/5-so-do-chien-thuat-giup-argentina-ha-nigeria-de-mo-ve-di-tiep-421-189628.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/26/5-so-do-chien-thuat-giup-argentina-ha-nigeria-de-mo-ve-di-tiep.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/5-so-do-chien-thuat-giup-argentina-ha-nigeria-de-mo-ve-di-tiep-421-189628.html\">5 s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt gi\u00fap Argentina h\u1ea1 Nigeria \u0111\u1ec3 m\u01a1 v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp</span><br>\r\nTr\u1eadn h\u00f2a th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iceland v\u00e0 sau \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i th\u1ea3m h\u1ea1i 0-3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn Argentina c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i ngay sau v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1ea3ng. V\u1eady th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/messi-va-dong-doi-tich-cuc-tap-luyen-cho-tran-cau-sinh-tu-gap-nigeria-461-189597.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/26/messi-va-dong-doi-tich-cuc-tap-luyen-cho-tran-cau-sinh-tu-gap-nigeria.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/messi-va-dong-doi-tich-cuc-tap-luyen-cho-tran-cau-sinh-tu-gap-nigeria-461-189597.html\">Messi v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i t\u00edch c\u1ef1c t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n cho tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u sinh t\u1eed g\u1eb7p Nigeria</span><br>\r\nBu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho tr\u1eadn quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh chi\u1ebfc v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp \u1edf World Cup 2018 c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n Argentina luy\u1ec7n t\u1eadp di\u1ec5n ra trong b\u1ea7u kh\u00f4ng kh\u00ed tr\u1ea7m l\u1eafng.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hlv-argentina-tin-messi-se-toa-sang-truoc-nigeria-421-189588.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/22/hlv-argentina-tin-messi-se-toa-sang-truoc-nigeria.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hlv-argentina-tin-messi-se-toa-sang-truoc-nigeria-421-189588.html\">HLV Argentina tin Messi s\u1ebd t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nigeria</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb tr\u01b0\u1edbc gi\u1edd b\u00f3ng l\u0103n, HLV Sampaoli ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n tin t\u01b0\u1edfng ng\u00f4i sao s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t \u0110T Argentina l\u00fac n\u00e0y Lionel Messi s\u1ebd bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Nigeria...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hlv-nigeria-len-tieng-de-doa-argentina-421-189586.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/22/hlv-nigeria-len-tieng-de-doa-argentina.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hlv-nigeria-len-tieng-de-doa-argentina-421-189586.html\">HLV Nigeria l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng \u0111e d\u1ecda Argentina</span><br>\r\nHLV Gernot Rohr n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Nigeria vs Argentina, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y 64 tu\u1ed5i t\u1ef1 tin c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Nam M\u1ef9.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div>\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"601","checkdouble":"189635"},{"date":"16:49 26/06","title":"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP Australia vs Peru 21h00 ng\u00e0y 26/6 (World Cup 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/26/truc-tiep-australia-vs-peru.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Australia vs Peru: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Peru vs Australia b\u1ea3ng C World Cup 2018 l\u00fac 21h00 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 26/6.</h2><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Australia vs Peru: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Peru vs Australia b\u1ea3ng C World Cup 2018 l\u00fac 21h00 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 26/6.</h2>\r\nB\u1ecb l\u1ed7i, vui l\u00f2ng click t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/truc-tiep-australia-vs-peru-463-189637.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 0, 0);\"><u><strong>TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP AUSTRALIA VS PERU</strong></u></span></span><br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"600","checkdouble":"189637"},{"date":"16:55 26/06","title":"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP \u0110an M\u1ea1ch vs Ph\u00e1p 21h00 ng\u00e0y 26/6 (World Cup 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/26/truc-tiep-dan-mach-vs-phap.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp \u0110an M\u1ea1ch vs Ph\u00e1p: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Ph\u00e1p vs \u0110an M\u1ea1ch b\u1ea3ng C World Cup 2018 l\u00fac 21h00 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 26/6.</h2><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp \u0110an M\u1ea1ch vs Ph\u00e1p: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Ph\u00e1p vs \u0110an M\u1ea1ch b\u1ea3ng C World Cup 2018 l\u00fac 21h00 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 26/6.</h2>\r\nB\u1ecb l\u1ed7i, vui l\u00f2ng click v\u00e0o \u0111\u00e2y <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/truc-tiep-dan-mach-vs-phap-463-189638.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 0, 0);\"><u><strong>TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP PH\u00c1P VS \u0110AN M\u1ea0CH</strong></u></span></span><br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"599","checkdouble":"189638"},{"date":"09:14 26/06","title":"HLV Nigeria l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng \u0111e d\u1ecda Argentina","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/22/hlv-nigeria-len-tieng-de-doa-argentina.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Gernot Rohr n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Nigeria vs Argentina, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y 64 tu\u1ed5i t\u1ef1 tin c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Nam M\u1ef9.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chung k\u1ebft b\u1ea3ng D gi\u1eefa Nigeria v\u00e0 Argentina</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nArgentina d\u00f9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng D World Cup 2018 nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea1i g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn. \u1ede tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 h\u00f2a 1-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iceland, sau \u0111\u00f3 Messi v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i thua s\u1ed1c 0-3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Gernot Rohr n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Nigeria vs Argentina h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Gernot Rohr n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Nigeria vs Argentina h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/26/HLV-Gernot-Rohr-noi-ve-tran-Nigeria-vs-Argentina-hinh-anh.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u00a0Nigeria vs Argentina \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i b\u1ea3ng D World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nR\u1ea5t may cho Argentina l\u00e0 Nigeria \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap h\u1ecd th\u1eafp s\u00e1ng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp. Theo \u0111\u00f3 \u201c\u0110\u1ea1i b\u00e0ng xanh\u201d sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 0-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Iceland \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 2.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ee5c di\u1ec7n b\u1ea3ng D l\u00fac n\u00e0y ngo\u00e0i Croatia th\u00ec 3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f2n kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111i ti\u1ebfp. Croatia \u0111ang d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi 6 \u0111i\u1ec3m, Nigeria x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 2 v\u1edbi 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u00f2n Argentina v\u00e0 Iceland m\u1ed7i \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f3 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u1ed1i nay, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-nigeria-vs-argentina-1h00-ngay-276-vua-da-bong-vua-cau-nguyen-421-189578.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nigeria vs Argentina</span> trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong hai \u0111\u1ed9i n\u1ebfu c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng th\u00ec c\u00e1nh c\u1eeda \u0111i ti\u1ebfp s\u1ebd r\u1ed9ng m\u1edf.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nN\u1ebfu Nigeria gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc Argentina, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111i ti\u1ebfp m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Croatia v\u00e0 Iceland. Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, n\u1ebfu Argentina gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m h\u1ecd c\u0169ng c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>HLV Nigeria \u0111e d\u1ecda Argentina</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Gernot Rohr n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Nigeria vs Argentina, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y 64 tu\u1ed5i t\u1ef1 tin c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Nam M\u1ef9.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Gernot Rohr phat bieu ve tran Nigeria vs Iceland\" title=\"Gernot Rohr ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Nigeria vs Iceland\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/23/hlv-nigeria-hay-mang-argentina-den-day.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Gernot Rohr ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Nigeria vs Argentina</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd b\u1eb1ng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iceland, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111ang c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Argentina. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng, n\u00f3 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u1ebfn c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i, b\u1edfi v\u1eady to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111ang r\u1ea5t t\u1eadp trung\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cV\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 11 n\u0103m 2017 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Argentina 4-2, Nigeria t\u1ef1 tin c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng v\u00e0 b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, b\u1edfi v\u1eady ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn Nigeria s\u1ebd h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"598","checkdouble":"189586"},{"date":"09:29 26/06","title":"Marco Reus n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau khi \u0111\u1ea9y Mesut Ozil l\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/24/marco-reus-noi-gi-sau-khi-day-mesut-ozil-len-bang-ghe-du-bi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Marco Reus ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Mesut Ozil, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Dortmund \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao t\u1ea7m quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Marco Reus \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao Mesut Ozil</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMesut Ozil \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh tr\u01b0\u1edbc Mexico nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u00ec nhi\u1ec1u, ch\u00ednh phong \u0111\u1ed9 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a anh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn C\u1ed7 xe t\u0103ng \u0111\u1ec3 thua 0-1. Ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb HLV Low tr\u1eebng ph\u1ea1t sau m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Marco Reus ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Mesut Ozil h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Marco Reus ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Mesut Ozil h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/24/marco-reus-noi-gi-sau-khi-day-mesut-ozil-len-bang-ghe-du-bi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Reus \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao s\u1ef1 quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a Ozil v\u1edbi \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 2 c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ee9c \u1edf b\u1ea3ng F V\u1edbi Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n \u00f4ng Low \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Marco Reus \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed h\u1ed9 c\u00f4ng thay v\u00ec Mesut Ozil, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1988 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u1ed9t ph\u00fat n\u00e0o.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/marco-reus-noi-gi-sau-ban-thang-dau-tien-o-world-cup-421-189402.html\" target=\"_blank\">Marco Reus khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t</span>, anh g\u00f3p d\u1ea5u gi\u00e0y v\u00e0o c\u1ea3 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ee9c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n. \u0110\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, Reus ghi b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a 1-1, sau \u0111\u00f3 anh ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o gi\u00fap Toni Kroos ghi b\u00e0n \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-1 cho \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Dortmund s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh thay v\u00ec Ozil. Marco Reus ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Mesut Ozil, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Dortmund \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao t\u1ea7m quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;Anh \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c, anh \u1ea5y v\u1eabn \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 quan tr\u1ecdng trong k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch c\u1ee7a HLV Low. Ozil l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, t\u00f4i tin r\u1eb1ng anh \u1ea5y s\u1ebd th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u1edf nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Reus tin \u0110\u1ee9c s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n, \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1edf b\u1ea3ng F. Hi\u1ec7n Mexico \u0111ang d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y v\u1edbi 6 \u0111i\u1ec3m, \u0110\u1ee9c v\u00e0 Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n x\u1ebfp sau v\u1edbi 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u00f2n H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0o.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Reus va man tro lai tuyet voi\" title=\"Reus v\u00e0 m\u00e0n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/24/marco-reus-noi-gi-sau-ban-thang-dau-tien-o-world-cup.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Reus tin \u0110\u1ee9c s\u1ebd c\u00f3 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i \u0110\u1ee9c s\u1ebd c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, C\u1ed7 xe t\u0103ng bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ec3 hy v\u1ecdng \u0111i ti\u1ebfp. Marco Reus kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb r\u1ea5t k\u1ef9 cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111ang quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;\u0110\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i, \u0110\u1ee9c bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i t\u1ef1 tin c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd l\u00e0m t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"597","checkdouble":"189587"},{"date":"09:18 26/06","title":"HLV Argentina tin Messi s\u1ebd t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nigeria","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/22/hlv-argentina-tin-messi-se-toa-sang-truoc-nigeria.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Thanh H\u00f3a vs H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng l\u00fac 17h00 ng\u00e0y 26/6 (V\u00f2ng 16 gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG Vi\u1ec7t Nam V-League 2018): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Thanh H\u00f3a vs H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng 17h00 ng\u00e0y 266 (V-League 2018) h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Thanh H\u00f3a vs H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng 17h00 ng\u00e0y 266 (V-League 2018) h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/26/truc-tiep-flc-thanh-hoa-vs-hai-phong.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Thanh H\u00f3a vs H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> Thanh H\u00f3a vs H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng: 1-0<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\nTr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i V-League 2018 gi\u1eefa Thanh H\u00f3a vs H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng m\u1edbi di\u1ec5n ra h\u00f4m 8/6 v\u1eeba qua. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m Thanh H\u00f3a \u0111ang r\u01a1i v\u00e0o kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng sau khi thanh l\u00fd m\u1ed9t l\u00fac 3 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t. K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n d\u01b0\u1edbi quy\u1ec1n HLV Nguy\u1ec5n \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng b\u1ecb H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 0-2 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n L\u1ea1ch Tray.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u0111\u00f3, Thanh H\u00f3a \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ed3i sinh m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd. V\u0169 Minh Tu\u1ea5n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i sau ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, H\u1eefu D\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 t\u1eeb C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1, Thanh H\u00f3a c\u00e0ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00e0ng kh\u1edfi s\u1eafc. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Thanh \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 3 th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi 9 \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ed1i \u0111a sau 3 tr\u1eadn, Thanh H\u00f3a leo m\u1ed9t m\u1ea1ch l\u00ean v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 5 tr\u00ean BXH, ch\u1ec9 k\u00e9m v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 4 c\u1ee7a H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng \u0111\u00fang 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m. Thanh H\u00f3a hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ngh\u0129 t\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i \u00c1 qu\u00e2n khi kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch gi\u1eefa h\u1ecd v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00ec b\u1ea3ng Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng c\u00f3 3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u00ean 5 v\u00f2ng g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y - m\u1ed9t th\u00e0nh t\u00edch kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed3i. D\u1eabu v\u1eady, m\u00f9a n\u00e0y, \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n d\u01b0\u1edbi quy\u1ec1n HLV Tr\u01b0\u01a1ng Vi\u1ec7t Ho\u00e0ng l\u1ea1i thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed1t khi ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch. 5 tr\u1eadn xa nh\u00e0 v\u1eeba qua, H\u1ea3i P\u00f2ng ch\u1ec9 th\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 1 tr\u1eadn tr\u01b0\u1edbc S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC, c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 3 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i v\u00e0 1 tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a. B\u1edfi v\u1eady, tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t Thanh H\u00f3a \u0111ang h\u1ed3i sinh \u0111\u1ea7y m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd, H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng kh\u00f3 h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec3m ra v\u1ec1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn:<br>\r\nThanh H\u00f3a: Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng; \u0110\u00ecnh \u0110\u1ed3ng, V\u0103n Nam, Minh T\u00f9ng, Xu\u00e2n H\u01b0ng, H\u1eefu D\u0169ng, Tr\u1ecdng Ho\u00e0ng, Ho\u00e0ng Th\u1ecbnh, Minh Tu\u1ea5n, \u0110\u00ecnh T\u00f9ng, Omar.<br>\r\nH\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng: V\u0103n L\u00e2m; Ho\u00e0i D\u01b0\u01a1ng, Schmidt, Ho\u00e0ng D\u01b0\u01a1ng, Qu\u1ed1c Trung, Anh H\u00f9ng, Ng\u1ecdc T\u00e2n, Th\u00e0nh Long, Stevens, Fagan, \u0110\u00ecnh B\u1ea3o.</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"596","checkdouble":"189588"},{"date":"09:55 26/06","title":"MU s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng trao \u0111\u1ed5i \"bom t\u1ea5n\" v\u1edbi PSG","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/26/mu-san-sang-trao-doi-bom-tan-voi-psg.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>MU mu\u1ed1n mua Marco Verratti, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn d\u00f9ng Paul Pogba \u0111\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">MU quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m mua Verratti</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Carrick gi\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec7, Mourinho \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p. R\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Marco Verratti c\u1ee7a PSG.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Hy sinh Pogba, MU mu\u1ed1n mua Marco Verratti b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Hy sinh Pogba, MU mu\u1ed1n mua Marco Verratti b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/14/Hy-sinh-Pogba,-MU-muon-mua-Marco-Verratti-bang-duoc-o-He-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>MU mu\u1ed1n mua Verratti\u00a0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t ch\u00e2u \u00c2u. Marco Verratti c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00e2n ph\u1ed1i v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u ti\u1ebft tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi, anh c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao \u1edf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00e1t \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 s\u00fat xa.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi PSG, b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi s\u00e2n C\u00f4ng vi\u00ean c\u00e1c Ho\u00e0ng t\u1eed.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede H\u00e8 2017, su\u00fdt ch\u00fat n\u1eefa Barca \u0111\u00e3 mua th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ng\u00f4i sao 26 tu\u1ed5i, th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ed5 b\u1ec3 khi Barca ch\u1ec9 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn tr\u1ea3 80 tri\u1ec7u euro trong khi PSG \u0111\u00f2i \u0111\u1ee7 100 tri\u1ec7u euro cho ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMourinho \u0111ang khao kh\u00e1t Verratti, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 mu\u1ed1n M.U ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi \u0111\u1eadm cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi \u0111\u1ee7 100 tri\u1ec7u euro nh\u01b0 ph\u00eda PSG y\u00eau c\u1ea7u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>M.U c\u00f3 th\u00eam c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Verratti</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/mu-mua-verratti-voi-gia-75-trieu-bang-172-187639.html\" target=\"_blank\">MU mu\u1ed1n mua Marco Verratti</span>, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn d\u00f9ng Paul Pogba \u0111\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"MU san sang doi Pogba lay Verratti\" title=\"MU s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ed5i Pogba l\u1ea5y Verratti\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/26/mu-san-sang-trao-doi-bom-tan-voi-psg.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>MU s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ed5i Pogba l\u1ea5y Verratti</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo \u0111\u00f3, M.U s\u1ebd g\u1eedi 2 l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb t\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p. Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 100 tri\u1ec7u euro ho\u1eb7c \u0111\u1ed5i Pogba l\u1ea5y c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia. Cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Pogba v\u00e0 Mourinho c\u00f3 m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn, b\u1edfi v\u1eady \u00f4ng n\u00e0y s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p ra \u0111i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nVerratti d\u00f9 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi v\u1edbi PSG nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p. Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng PSG s\u1ebd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn trao \u0111\u1ed5i ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u1edbi M.U, tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p c\u0169ng nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m v\u1edbi Pogba.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"595","checkdouble":"189590"},{"date":"10:22 26/06","title":"Sao Arsenal quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m ti\u1ec5n Messi v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1edbm","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/26/sao-arsenal-quyet-tam-tien-messi-ve-nuoc-som.PNG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Alex Iwobi ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Nigeria vs Argentina, ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Arsenal t\u1ef1 tin s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn Messi v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i ph\u1ea3i l\u00ean m\u00e1y bay tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1edbm.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp m\u1edf ra v\u1edbi Nigeria</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean b\u1ea3ng D World Cup 2018, Nigeria \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi thua Croatia 0-2. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u Phi \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t, song kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu k\u00e9m khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Alex Iwobi ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Nigeria vs Argentina h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Alex Iwobi ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Nigeria vs Argentina h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/23/Alex-Iwobi-phat-bieu-ve-tran-Nigeria-vs-Argentina-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nigeria th\u1eafp s\u00e1ng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iceland</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 2 g\u1eb7p Iceland, Nigeria \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i trong 45 ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean. Tuy nhi\u00ean s\u1ef1 b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 trong hi\u1ec7p thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 2 gi\u00fap h\u1ecd c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-0. 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u00fap \u201c\u0110\u1ea1i b\u00e0ng xanh\u201d th\u1eafp l\u1ea1i c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ee5c di\u1ec7n b\u1ea3ng D l\u00fac n\u00e0y ngo\u00e0i Croatia ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u0111i ti\u1ebfp th\u00ec Nigeria, Argentina v\u00e0 Iceland \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp. \u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, Nigeria s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 Argentina, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i \u1edf b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nN\u1ebfu Nigeria gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc Argentina, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/hlv-nigeria-len-tieng-de-doa-argentina-421-189586.html\" target=\"_blank\">HLV Gernot Rohr n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Nigeria vs Argentina</span>, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y 64 tu\u1ed5i t\u1ef1 tin c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Nam M\u1ef9 qua \u0111\u00f3 gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Iwobi c\u0169ng tin Nigeria \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c h\u1ea1 Argentina</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Alex Iwobi ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Nigeria vs Argentina, ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Arsenal t\u1ef1 tin s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn Messi v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i ph\u1ea3i l\u00ean m\u00e1y bay tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1edbm.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Iwobi phat bieu ve tran Nigeria vs Argentina\" title=\"Iwobi ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Nigeria vs Argentina\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/26/sao-arsenal-quyet-tam-tien-messi-ve-nuoc-som.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Iwobi ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Nigeria vs Argentina</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111ang r\u1ea5t t\u1ef1 tin sau khi gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iceland, Nigeria c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee7 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc Argentina. NHM \u0111ang k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0o Nigeria v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ecd ph\u1ea3i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cArgentina l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn, h\u1ecd c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, song Nigeria l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 \u0111o\u00e0n k\u1ebft, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u0169ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u1ecfi. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111ang r\u1ea5t t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Argentina \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng ti\u1ebfp theo\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"594","checkdouble":"189591"}]}